high_descs: Turn around and go across to the sink.
Open the cabinet on the left and pick up the salt shaker.
Turn around and stand back at the sink.
Put the salt shaker on the counter in front of the spoon.
Look up at the cabinet above the counter.
Open the cabinet on the left and pick up the salt shaker.
Turn completely around and face towards the sink.
Put the salt shaker beside the spoon on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers on the counter.

high_descs: Go to the sink
Get a salt shaker from the cupboard to the right of the sink
Turn around in a 360
Place the salt shaker on the counter to the right of the sink
Look up at the cupboard next to the sink
Take a salt shaker from the cupboard
Turn around in a 360
Place the salt shaker on the counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Move two salt shakers from a cupboard to a countertop

high_descs: Turn around, turn to the right, walk one step before tuning to the right again and walk straight to the sink. Look up to the cabinet to your tight.
Open the door of the cabinet, pick up the salt at the back and close the cabinet.
Look down to the counter top under the cabinet.
Put the salt on the counter top, in front of the yellow knife.
Look up to the cabinet on top of the counter top again.
Open the door of the cabinet, pick up another salt and close the cabinet.
Look down to the counter top under the cabinet again.
Put the other salt on top of the counter top, in front of the other knife.
anns.task_desc: Put 2 salt in front of the 2 knives on the counter top.
